commit.message:
Merge pull request #10 from tarsius/master

Add file vendor/.nosearch

Add file vendor/.nosearch

This helps keeping "vendor/" of the `load-path'
and helps tools that extract dependency information.

Specify argument in mock call.

Fixes #8
Add usage information for specific commands.
Change argument name and update doc-string.
Use princ with newline instead of message.
Do not duplicate flags in usage information.
Add syntax highlighting for code examples in README.

Add support for auto docs.

Not specifying description will use the function doc-string as description.

Use push with nreverse instead of add-to-list.

This should not change any functionality, but there are bugs in Emacs
24.1 and 24.2 that are hard to find the cause for. This is an attempt to
fix it.

This is also better because it allows for lexical binding if we want to
enable it in the future.
